title: Miau Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Mediterranean, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Coffee and cake cafe that's a shelter for homeless cats. Has vegan options on the menu. For breakfast sandwiches with hummus, dried tomatoes and arugula, with vegan "cottage cheese," sunflower and leek and classic and curry hummus with baguette. In a fridge there is always plant-based milks supply and sometimes date cookies.
